high_descs: Turn to your left and go past the couch, to the end of the room, turn right at the lamp and go to the first chair on the left side of the table.
Pick up the book on the table, in front of the chair.
Turn to your right and go back around the table, into the living room, then turn left between the couch and the coffee table and face the couch to your left.
Place the book on the left cushion of the couch.
anns.task_desc: Put a book on the couch.

high_descs: Turn around and turn left going between the black table and the black couch. Stay to the right of the dining set with blue chairs.
Pick up the green book from the dining set with blue chairs.
Circle right back around the dining set with blue chairs and pass the black table on your right turning left after the black couch.
Put the green book on the left side of the black couch.
anns.task_desc: Pick up the green book and put it on the black couch.

high_descs: walk to the dining room table to face a book with a rhinoceros on it
pick up the book with a rhino on it from the dining room table
put the book upside down on the sofa
anns.task_desc: put a book on a sofa
